== 事件 ==
=== 爆發登革熱疫情 公園需關閉 ===
2018年8月，香港突然新增大量[[登革熱|登革熱]]個案，確診人數破歷來紀錄<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180823/bkn-20180823172214259-0823_00822_001.html|title=登革熱再增4宗共23宗破紀錄　長洲夫婦齊中招|author=|date=2018-08-23|work=東方日報|accessdate=|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613101319/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180823/bkn-20180823172214259-0823_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。追查後，發現大部份病人曾到訪獅子山公園<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180823/20482522|title=長洲兩登革熱患者  疑清理塌樹被蚊叮|author=|date=2018-08-23|work=蘋果日報|accessdate=|archive-date=2019-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606141609/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180823/20482522|dead-url=no}}</ref>，公園因此被相信是感染源頭<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180817/s00001/1534504223597|title=獅子山公園今晚7時起關閉30天　政府將跨部門全港大滅蚊|author=|date=2018-08-17|work=明報|accessdate=|archive-date=2018-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180817161415/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180817/s00001/1534504223597|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府相信[[白紋伊蚊|白紋伊蚊]]已將病毒傳播至下一代，於8月17日決定封閉獅子山公園<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201808/17/P2018081700996.htm|title=獅子山公園暫時關閉|author=|date=2018-08-17|work=香港政府新聞網|accessdate=|archive-date=2019-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191110062349/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201808/17/P2018081700996.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=316943|title=政府下午跨部門會議討論暫時關閉獅子山公園|author=|date=2018-08-17|work=now新聞|accessdate=|language=zh-yue|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603110352/https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=316943|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月10日，隨著最後一宗新發現個案距今已有30天，[[衞生署_(香港)|衛生署]]宣布疫情結束<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181010/s00001/1539178192350 |title=衛生署：本地登革熱疫情完結 |date=2018-10-10 |work=明報 |accessdate=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2018-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011115334/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181010/s00001/1539178192350 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.tvb.com/local/5bc1cc8fe6038390082310b2/ |title=本地登革熱疫情結束 政府稱經科學數據及臨床確定 |date=2018-10-13 |work=無綫新聞 |language=zh-yue |accessdate=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611205002/http://news.tvb.com/local/5bc1cc8fe6038390082310b2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，公園最終於10月13日重新開放。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422757-20181012.htm|title=康文署宣布獅子山公園明日上午9時重新開放|author=|date=2018-10-12|work=香港電台|accessdate=2018-10-12|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012213153/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1422757-20181012.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181013/s00001/1539409271335 |title=多圖 獅子山公園重開　園圃經歷山竹一片凌亂　燒烤場冷清 |date=2018-10-13 |work=明報 |accessdate=2018-10-14 |archive-date=2018-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181013095643/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181013/s00001/1539409271335 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

